Google Play Privacy Policy

"Remake A Famous Game with Zombie" is an android app that I made using Unity game engine and purely for my own educational purpose.
the app is not made for commercial purpose and contain no active ads. Or in other word the developer of this app did not included any ads or any way to make money inside this app.
However due to it is made by using Unity game engine and on Android platform , they can contain passive ads or automatically collect your device information outside of the developer's control

